      "content": "that makes sense. so when i'm writing the conclusion, i want to wrap it up by saying that wealth redistribution isnt just one option among many, but actually the only just and moral path forward if we care about equality. does that sound like a strong way to end it? or is there a way to phrase it so it sounds like an absolute necessity rather than just a suggestion?",
